### Variables (replace with real IDs after seeding – get eventId and seatIds from GET events/:id/seats)
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@eventId = {{eventId}}
@seatIds = {{seatIds}}
@reservationId = {{reservationId}}
@token = {{token}}

### ========== RESERVATIONS ==========

### Lock seats (creates pending reservation – requires CLIENT role)
# Use eventId and available seat IDs from GET events/:id/seats
POST {{baseUrl}}/reservations/lock
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "eventId": "{{eventId}}",
  "seatIds": ["{{seatIds}}"]
}

### Get my reservations (requires CLIENT role)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reservations/my-reservations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get reservation by ID (requires CLIENT or ORGANIZER role)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reservations/{{reservationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Confirm reservation (after payment – requires CLIENT role)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/reservations/{{reservationId}}/confirm
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Cancel reservation (only PENDING – requires CLIENT role)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/reservations/{{reservationId}}/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
